<div class="title">Experiments</div>
<div class="substance">Amanita muscaria & Cannabis</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=GW&Exact=1">GW</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; GW. "Experiments: An Experience with Amanita muscaria & Cannabis (exp9552)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Oct 3, 2001. erowid.org/exp/9552</div>

